KChange

A utility used for keeping track of changes. 

The program allows you to create an unlimited number of projects to which you can be logging changes.

It allows you to add files related to the project and indicate changes on specific files.

Also allows you to generate a ChangeLog file - (.TXT, .CSV)

Future plans:

Add possibility for the user to use a remote database, for collaboration.

Clean-up some undocumented code

Add exception handling